## Approach
Walk Flutter's semantics tree from `WidgetsBinding.instance.pipelineOwner.semanticsOwner` and emit compact JSON records `{id, role, label, state, actions, rect}`. Maintain `Map<int, int>` from `SemanticsNode.id` to host-stable id so the same node carries the same id across captures within a session. Filter off-screen, `isHidden`/`excludeSemantics`, and fully-obscured nodes by default. Register `ext.flutter.exploration.core.get_semantics` on `ExplorationBinding` (cx6.2). Schema is consumed verbatim by cx6.6 (action targets), cx6.8 (core fragment), cx6.10 (diagnostic).

## Constraints
- Stable ids per session (PRD ¬ß11.1, ¬ß12.3); not cross-session.
- Plain JSON; web-reachable harness.
- Fits 4KB core budget (PRD ¬ß11.4): omit empty fields, integer rects.
- kDebugMode/kProfileMode gating via `ExplorationBinding`.

## Ruled out
- v0.2 `isInteractiveWidget` host hook (custom-design-system widgets are a plugin concern in v0.5, PRD ¬ß6.1).
- Off-screen nodes by default (use `core.scroll_until_visible` in cx6.6).
- Raw `SemanticsData` blob.

