## Approach
`ExplorationBinding extends WidgetsFlutterBinding` with `ensureInitialized({required List<ExplorationPlugin> plugins})`. Installs as singleton, hard-fails on foreign binding, no-ops outside debug/profile, registers `ext.flutter.exploration.core.handshake`. Registry deferred to cx6.3 ‚Äî this bead stores the plugin list verbatim. cx6.2 introduces a minimal `ExplorationPlugin` placeholder (`namespace` only); cx6.3 extends it additively (non-breaking per PRD ¬ß7.7). Anchors: PRD ¬ß6.1, ¬ß6.5, ¬ß7.6, ¬ß17, ¬ß22.

